This paper is about deep neural networks and their ability to perform complex reasoning tasks. The paper specifically focuses on Memory Networks (MemNNs) and Relation Networks (RNs) and introduces a new architecture called Working Memory Networks. Given that the paper deals with deep learning and reasoning, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI. Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (machine learning), cs.CL (computational linguistics), cs.CV (computer vision), and cs.NE (neural and evolutionary computing).
